Package for all performance tests - or "benchmarks" as they say.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChronicleMapBaselineBenchmark
    Offers a number of baseline benchmarks for ChronicleMapRealBenchmark.
    ChronicleMapRealBenchmark
    Benchmarks Chronicle Map using different serialization frameworks.
    ConstructFastMoneyBenchmark
    If we already have the long number we know FastMoney store internally, then is it faster to use the public API or reflection to create an instance of FastMoney?

    If performance matter, how would you create an instance of Money?
    MemoryUsageProfiler
    Will log the memory used after each iteration.
    ReadFastMoneyNumberBenchmark
